Wheeljack-X::

"First of all, hang on to this."  Jackie hands him the skewer with the 
veggies on it.  "I need both hands free.  The deal is, we need to find 
a host for Blackfang's spark - a volunteer to keep it running while I 
work on his head.  It's risky, and I'd appreciate it if you made sure 
that only someone who understands the hazards volunteers to host the 
spark."
